= vim & haskell =
See also:
[[topic/tags]]

== which features are worth supporting?
* ghci
* cabal
* haddock
* searches Hoogle and Hayoo

== which plugins exist

* [[http://projects.haskell.org/haskellmode-vim/|haskellmode-vim]]

* [[http://github.com/MarcWeber/vim-addon-haskell|vim-addon-haskel]]: 
  (run cabal using vim-addon-actions, has some more magic to
  add -X compiler flags by parsing compiler errors, reconfigures your cabal
  project, allows you to choose a build configuration)

* [[https://github.com/travitch/hasksyn|hasksyn]]
  which is a rewrite of [[https://github.com/dag/vim2hs|dag/vim2hs]]

* [[https://github.com/ujihisa/neco-ghc|neco-ghc]]

(Maybe more)
